      <h1>§6.4 Sovereign Interface Standards</h1>
      <p class="dp-cover-desc">
        Visual consistency in a CBDC environment is not merely aesthetic — it is a
        psychological indicator of stability and trust. A unified colour palette reduces
        cognitive load for operators handling billions in sovereign digital assets and
        ensures that every entry point, from the Authentication Gateway to the Issuance
        Desk, reads as a single hardened system.
      </p>
      <div class="dp-cover-meta">
        <div>Version <b>1.0</b></div>
        <div>Palette <b>Sovereign Navy</b></div>
        <div>Status <b>Enforced</b></div>
        <div>Scope <b>Qt6 Desktop · All Modules</b></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

